Description: Fragment of a pottery amphora handle; five narrow ribs on the outside; smooth on underside. Hard, light yellow/brown/grey clay, Munsell 2.5YR 7/2 (light grey).
Bibliographic references: Weber 2012 / Untersuchungen zur archaischen griechischen Keramik aus anderen ägyptischen Fundorten (TD 318)
Acquisition notes: Found unregistered in the Department in 2010, in a box with other sherds from Tell Dafana.
